{
  "chapter": 292,
  "chapter_summary": "本章为《寻秦记》终章，分为两大部分。前半部分以史笔叙述嬴政扫除吕不韦和嫪毐后采纳李斯、尉缭之计，逐一灭韩、赵、燕、魏、楚、齐六国，统一天下，自号始皇帝，建立三十六郡、统一度量衡等制度，并筑怀清台以怀念项少龙。后半部分为后记，项少龙与乌卓、滕翼、荆俊在草原策骑牧马，纪嫣然、琴清、乌廷芳等妻儿在营地等候。众人欢聚之际，项宝儿改名\"项羽\"，项少龙闻言震惊，意识到自己的\"儿子\"正是日后与刘邦争天下的楚霸王。他最终释然，感悟成败并不重要，轰轰烈烈活过便是不负此生。全书在项少龙策马追赶\"项羽\"等孩子的壮丽画面中完结。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "兄弟们！看你们的本领哩！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 87
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_wu_zhuo",
      "text": "大哥真懂得拣地方，这里处处均得大小河流灌溉，水源充沛，土壤肥沃，牧草茂盛，确是人间胜境。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_zhuo",
      "speaker_name": "乌卓",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "当年我初抵此处，心中颇有点我们是被迫自我放逐的味儿。但现在长居下来，杀了我都不肯离开这里。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_jun",
      "speaker_name": "荆俊",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那头纯白的！我要那头纯白的！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这小子，丹儿已为他生下三个儿子、两个女儿，仍然像个长不大的孩子。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_qing",
      "speaker_name": "琴清",
      "listener": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "text": "夫君大人回来哩！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁愿随我去迎接我们凯旋的战士？",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老天爷待我们非常优厚，以前哪想过真可过着这种无忧无虑的幸福日子。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_qing",
      "speaker_name": "琴清",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "要有我们那种经历的，方会明白这种草原生活的珍贵，像宝儿那小家伙，就常嚷着要回中原去见识世面。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ting_fang",
      "speaker_name": "乌廷芳",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "以后你最好不要再给他说中原的事，尤其是有关楚国的，宝儿最欢喜就是那里，真令人费解。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "每个人总有他的梦想，因为我们的梦想已成为事实，所以乐于安享梦想，宝儿只是在追寻他的梦想罢了！我们既不该阻止，更不应强要他安于我们的梦想。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "夫君说得真动听，宝儿的梦想是要变成天上的飞鹰，可随意翱翔，飞到大地任何一角去。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "赵致",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "人人都宠得他要命，我说呢！小贞和小凤就宠得他太过分了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 155
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "差点忘记告诉你这做人爹的，宝儿嫌自己的名字太过孩子气，要改过另一个名字。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "改什么名字也可以，只要是姓项就成。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 165
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ting_fang",
      "speaker_name": "乌廷芳",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "宝儿可是我取的，是他的乳名嘛！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我见他这么爱鹰，便提议给他起个鹰的别字。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "项鹰！倒也不错啊！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_qing",
      "speaker_name": "琴清",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你这做父亲的真不知孩儿的想法，他嫌鹰字太过像禽兽，怕人笑他，自己改了个'羽'字。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你怎么了，项羽不好听吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "夫君大人不欢喜这名字吗？宝儿却非常欢喜，若你要他改别的名字，我们可不会和他说，你自己去跟他谈好了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_qing",
      "speaker_name": "琴清",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "夫君大人在想什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我想通了！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "三弟想通了什么呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "项宝儿以后就是项羽。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "这也须想通或想不通的吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "text": "我想通的是成又如何，败又如何。成功、失败根本无关重要的，只要轰轰烈烈地活过，在历史上留下千古不灭的美名，便不负此生！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 233
    }
  ],
